caption.p: Partial dependencies of the top six key predictors of (a) minimum temperature (in 째C) during the winter, (b) year, (c) maximum temperature the during winter (in 째C), (d) wind speeds during the intermediate season (in m/s), (e) maximum temperature during the intermediate season (in 째C) and (f) maximum temperature (in 째C) during the summer, in the residential sector.
